relevant_findings.general: Alert and oriented x3, no acute distress.
relevant_findings.HEENT: No scleral icterus, mucous membranes moist.
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, no murmurs, gallops, or rubs.
relevant_findings.pulmonary: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezes, rhonchi, or respiratory distress.
relevant_findings.abdominal: Soft, nondistended, appropriately tender at incision sites, no rebound or guarding, no palpable masses, incision sites dressed.
relevant_findings.extremities: No edema, warm and well perfused.
